            "text": "Here are a few of the top-rated skincare spas in Katy, Texas, based on the search results:\n\n*   **Katy Med Tech Spa:** This med spa is known for its dedication to customer service and personalized treatments. They offer a range of services, including facials, laser hair removal, and body contouring. First-time customer deals are available.\n*   **Luxe Medical Aesthetics:** This spa combines cutting-edge techniques and professional care with high-quality, medical-grade products. They focus on providing luxurious and effective formulations to protect and revitalize the skin.\n*   **Anita's Skin Care Clinic:** This clinic offers a variety of services with a holistic approach to skincare, customizing treatments to address individual skin concerns.\n*   **Skincare by Monik:** Located in Katy/Fulshear, this spa offers a range of services, including anti-aging treatments, acne facials, HydraFacials, microneedling, and microdermabrasion.\n*   **Luminous MediSpa Katy:** This med spa offers a wide range of services from skin treatments and facial rejuvenation to injectables and laser treatments. They emphasize science-backed treatments performed by licensed professionals.\n"
